::Prowl::

Prowl turns his head to look at Iron Raptor as he hears her question. 
Whatever was disturbing him seems to have lessened in intensity. His eyes 
rest on Iron Raptor's form for a split second and the feeling comes back.

"I'm fine," He says. He turns away from Iron Raptor and walks on into the 
forest, "Let's keep moving,"
